50:
Ah, I see... The curse of the sword...
He must've held quite the grudge
against Stella.
53:
Well? What are you waiting for?
Now's your chance to end it all.
61:
What's the matter? A sword that's
slain a dragon should be more than
enough to kill me! Come on... just a
little more!
76:
If you've got a death wish... you best
get in line.
91: Get out of my way, Nimbus...
95:
I must keep fighting... for as long as I
draw breath!
99:
...What? I'm just supposed to let you
die? That wasn't our deal, pal.
104: What else... would you have me do?
108:
Tell me, Nimbus... What am I
supposed to do?!
113:
Why... Why am I always the one left
behind?!
117:
He was just a boy! The burden I put
upon him... The burden that should
have been mine! I just...
122:
...I just wanted to see him grow! He
was meant to be our future, Nimbus!
128:
You might wanna clean out those
ears then, ya sorry excuse for a
Champion!
132:
Don't tell me you can't hear that
voice callin' out!
149: What are you waiting for? GO!
153:
There you have it... Just taggin' in for
my friend here.
157:
Whitetail... Merely one of Stella's
pets. What could you possibly hope
to accomplish?
163: In this world, you're at my mer
167:
Yeah, yeah. How about you get a
taste of the goods first before
writing them off?
172:
See, my body's taken its share of hits
in the past. It's gonna take more
than some old relic to keep me from
fighting!
178:
Now you and I are gonna dance
until the others are ready to tag
back in!
182: Yes... Yes! I can hear it!
186: The voice... It's calling out to me!
200: So... You, too, have finally come.
204:
Tell me, boy... Will you join the curse
of the sword?
